{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo wiſſas muhsas Deenas\naifeetzaur tawu Dusmibu/ mehs\npawaddam muhsus Gaddus ka\nweenu Paſakku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Muhsas Dsihtwibas Laiks\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "ſtahw ſeptindeſmits Gaddus/\njeb ja kas tohti ſtiprs irr/ aſton-\ndefmits Gaddus/ un winnas\nLabbuins irr Gruhtums un Beh-\ndas/ jo ta aiſeet ahtri/ un mehs\nſkreename nohſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "(Bet) kas atſihst tawas\nDusmibas Stiprumu? un ta-\nwn Apſkaſchann eekſch tawas\nBihjaſchanas?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Mahzi muhs muhtas\nDeenas taſkaitiht/ ka mehs gud-\nru Sirdi dabhujam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Atgreesees KUNGS at-\nkak pee muins/ zik ilgi tad tas\nbuhs? un effi taweem Kalpeem\nſchehligs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pee-ehdini muhs agri ar\ntawu Schehlaſtibu/ tad gawile-\nſim mehs/ un preezaſimees wiſſa\nmuhtu Laika.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Eepreezini muhs pehz\ntahm Deenahm/ fur tu muhs\napbehdiiajs / pehz teem Gad-\ndeem/ fur mehs effam Zaunumu\nredſeiſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Parahdi taweem Kalpeem\ntawus Darbus/ un tawu Goh-\ndu winnu Behrneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta KUNGA muhsu\nDeewa Laipniba lat pahr mums\npaleek/ un paſchkix pee mums\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XCI. Dseefma.\nIrr weena Eepreezinaſchanas Dseefma/ fa\nkas us ta Wiſu angſtaka Glahbſchannu\nfaſajhs/preeſch wiſadu Neelaini war d\nſchi buht: 1. Jo Deews pats irr tahd\nGlahbſchannu un Palihdsibu apfohlijs: 14\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ab eekſch ta Wiſu-au\nſtaka Patweruma febs\n(un) appakſch ta Wiſu\nwarrena Ehnas paleek/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas ſakta us to KUNG\nManna Patauſchana un ma\nna ſtipra Pils/ mans Deew\nus ko es zerreju.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo wiſsch iſglabbs te-\nno ta Meddineeka Walgeem/\nta kaitiga Mehka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſsch apſeggs tewi ar\nweem Spahrneem/ ir tu a\npakſch winna Spahrneem gei-\nſeeti / winna Pateejba irr p\nApſeggu un preeſchturamiah\nBrunnahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka tewi ne waijaga bi-\ntees preeſch tahs Nakts Beed-\nschanas/ preeſch tahs Bulta-\nkas Deena ſkaida.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Preeſch ta Mehra/ ka-\nTunsiba waſajabs/preeſch ta-\nSehrgas/ kas Deenas-Wid-\nfamaita.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jepſchu tuhſtoschi fahn-\ntewi kriht / un Defmits tuhſ-\nſchi pee tawas labbas Rohkas-\ntatſchu tas tew ne aiſkems.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu tikai ar tawam A-\nzim uſluhkott/ un redſeſi/ ka tee-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
